154
00:11:27,040 --> 00:11:30,715
<i>- (girl) What about this one, Jo?
- I was looking at this one.</i>

155
00:11:30,800 --> 00:11:33,155
"Dental practice. Four O levels."

156
00:11:33,240 --> 00:11:36,152
"Required to train for three years
as dental nurse."

157
00:11:36,240 --> 00:11:39,277
"Should have French and Spanish,
but not essential."

158
00:11:39,360 --> 00:11:43,114
<i>(girl) Yeah, who do you have to suck off
to get that one, then?</i>

159
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:52,156
'Ere, what's this one say?

160
00:11:55,240 --> 00:11:58,710
"MIF, 9.30-5.30. Young person
for general warehouse duties."

161
00:11:58,800 --> 00:12:01,872
"Must be able to speak
fluent Punjabi and Urdu."

162
00:12:01,960 --> 00:12:03,916
- You speak Urdu?
- No.

163
00:12:04,800 --> 00:12:06,836
Fucks your chances then, dunnit?

164
00:12:08,160 --> 00:12:09,878
