182
00:14:20,760 --> 00:14:23,558
- What's this?
- Centre punch. You never seen one?

183
00:14:23,640 --> 00:14:25,596
- No.
- T-bar?

184
00:14:25,680 --> 00:14:27,830
- What's that for?
- I'll show you.

185
00:14:31,440 --> 00:14:33,396
Take these, get 'em in the centre.

186
00:14:33,480 --> 00:14:37,996
Hide 'em - stick 'em up your arse.
Don't lose 'em! We get nicked, chuck 'em.

187
00:15:04,360 --> 00:15:07,511
Hey, all the new cars -
they got locks, proper locks.

188
00:15:07,600 --> 00:15:10,717
