ain't got the right-sized keys?

189
00:15:10,800 --> 00:15:12,916
Which one do you want?

190
00:15:13,000 --> 00:15:14,956
That one.

191
00:15:37,520 --> 00:15:39,476
- See? It's locked!
- Bollocks.

192
00:15:43,040 --> 00:15:44,996
- You want the keys?
- No.

193
00:15:46,040 --> 00:15:48,918
<i>- (starts car)
- Oh, that's sweet. That's sweet, man.</i>

194
00:15:49,000 --> 00:15:50,752
- Now get out.
- What?

195
00:15:50,840 --> 00:15:52,193
- Get out.
- What for?

196
00:15:52,280 --> 00:15:54,236
I been down the Jobcentre on the bus.

197
00:15:54,320 --> 00:15:58,154
We get back together, they'll suss us
and get my keys, so you fuckin' walk.

198
00:15:58,240 --> 00:16:00,196
I'm going to see some mates.

199
00:16:01,360 --> 00:16:03,316
<i>(revs engine)</i>

200
00:16:40,840 --> 00:16:42,796
<i>(Peter) Trevor!</i>

201
00:16:45,560 --> 00:16:46,913
Trevor!

202
00:16:53,160 --> 00:16:55,116
Take it back.

203
00:16:55,200 --> 00:16:57,555
- What?
- The car, Trevor. Take it back!

204
00:16:57,640 --> 00:17:01,633
- I don't know what you're talking about.
- I'm not bloody stupid. I saw you.

205
00:17:01,720 --> 00:17:04,029
You've nicked that bloody car,
so take it back!

206
00:17:04,120 --> 00:17:06,076
I ain't nicked no car!

207
00:17:06,160 --> 00:17:09,596
I saw you get out of it.
Now, I'm not blind or stupid.

208
00:17:09,680 --> 00:17:11,636
Now, take it back. Get rid of it!

209
00:17:13,160 --> 00:17:15,879
I'll get rid of it. But I ain't taking it back.

210
00:17:17,240 --> 00:17:18,912
Fine.

211
00:17:19,000 --> 00:17:20,956
But do just that.

212
00:17:33,760 --> 00:17:35,716
<i>(water runs in cistern)</i>

213
00:18:02,200 --> 00:18:04,589
<i>- You've known about it for two weeks!
- (girl #1) I haven't till now!</i>

214
00:18:04,680 --> 00:18:08,036
<i>- (girl #2) I been on a boat before.
- (man) Let's start loading.</i>

215
00:18:08,120 --> 00:18:11,271
<i>- (woman) At least come and have a look.
- (girl #1) What for?</i>

216
00:18:11,360 --> 00:18:14,318
<i>- (girl #2) I ain't scared.
- (girl #1) I know you ain't.</i>

217
00:18:14,400 --> 00:18:16,356
<i>(girl #2) He said I was.</i>

218
00:18:16,440 --> 00:18:19,910
<i>(man) I did not! I said if you were nervous,
you should have a look.</i>

219
00:18:20,000 --> 00:18:21,956
Trevor?

220
00:18:23,040 --> 00:18:24,996
Come through, will you?

221
00:18:25,360 --> 00:18:27,828
<i>(girl #1) Go, and bloody good luck to ya!</i>

222
00:18:39,240 --> 00:18:41,196
